com.mrcrayfish.device.api.task

Interface Callback


  • public interface Callback
    A simple interface to handle processing responses by Task. Callbacks are necessary for the updating of any UI component.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void execute(net.minecraft.nbt.NBTTagCompound nbt, boolean success)
      Executes the callback.

    • Method Detail

      • execute

        void execute(net.minecraft.nbt.NBTTagCompound nbt,
             boolean success)
        Executes the callback. You should perform any changes to your UI in this method. The NBT tag contains the same data as Task.processResponse(NBTTagCompound)'s tag does.
        Parameters:
        nbt - the response data
        success - if the Task performed it's intended action correctly.
